{"tid":1860374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我撐政府 唔洗完全封關","createTime":"2020-02-03T15:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T16:05:47.000Z","uid":32371,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6fdd746ce62dd822772429802563e5d516da84","tid":1860374,"uid":32371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"搞到真攬炒<br />\n其實睇落宜家肺炎係對老人殺傷力大啲，感染 危殆都係都老人多，真係爆一爆啲樓價又再跌，宜家迫到佢封幾個關，點解後生黃絲醫護要再推落去完全封關？黃絲宜家都顯示到有出過力<br />\n再罷落去個訴求應該係保障醫護安全，有咩事入政府數/再先級。如果佢真係完全封關，對個抗爭有咩好處？但係就風險好大。老豆搵仔咁果啲整停羅湖站我係支持嘅。<br />\n<br />\n宜家應該係大力出動文宣 話比大家知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撐政府 滅廢老</strong></span> 其實我宜家見到啲有錢藍絲廢老（唔知係唔係但好似係）出事嘅話真係好心涼，最怕係醫護手足出事。<br />\n要趕係爆發前傳到呢個信息<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯 撐政府 滅廢老</span><br />\n咁佢爆就真攬炒，唔爆令廢老心有餘悸"},{"pid":"82daf720fd25406b34524c55fcd6365142941b33","tid":1860374,"uid":188601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"3886321f1eb879f82395ca829ffd2312ce0944ae","tid":1860374,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"我支持封關<br />\n<br />\n特別係娶強國女人果班你返得強國住就咪撚扮可憐"},{"pid":"43d11438897e8fa71c117faa4345c38fbfad9b38","tid":1860374,"uid":32371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"咁宜家罷工封關有咁多人支持都係好嘅 <br />\n但係有可能係佢企硬然後最後社區爆發，跟著啲人就唔罷<br />\n所以做文宣真係好重要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">撐政府 滅廢老</span> 貼晒係啲藍絲選區"},{"pid":"80a6882dbb198b425723d44af7f2f357e055bb12","tid":1860374,"uid":189790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法"},{"pid":"169eeff89f246840d7f6175106dd15dad5db88bc","tid":1860374,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0eaf59f55be48bac7d0d7c699980b7ab6713eb","tid":1860374,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"慳返啲生果金廢老津貼<br />\n慳埋嘅錢唔單止東大嶼<br />\n整多個西大嶼都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fecfc60bbe35d158cfe1892219f7824ea17e3f","tid":1860374,"uid":132217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"最多當plan B , 反送中叫左三個月先撒回啦，而家叫封關差唔多架啦，癈老死得差唔多佢就封關啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c80024371423d1ce689d2c34adb5a1de766956","tid":1860374,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06fecfc60bbe35d158cfe1892219f7824ea17e3f","tid":1860374,"uid":132217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"最多當plan B , 反送中叫左三個月先撒回啦，而家叫封關差唔多架啦，癈老死得差唔多佢就封關啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5d22a42f956579c570bba18761fe1ec7c56480","tid":1860374,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"支那廢老冇一個無無辜 一定要死撚晒 同啲死黑警一齊含家產"}]}